videos.headline: Stephen F. Austin takes delay of game penalty in show of equality
videos.description: Players from Stephen F. Austin kneel in unison and take a delay of game penalty to send a message of equality for all.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stephen F. Austin takes delay of game penalty in show of equality) 2020/9/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rikel goes untouched to end zone for SFA touchdown
videos.description: Trae Self hits Lawton Rikel on a wide receiver screen and Rikel takes it 16 yards to the house for the first Lumberjacks touchdown of the season.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rikel goes untouched to end zone for SFA touchdown) 2020/9/5 ESHEET
